<a name="browsable"></a>
<h3><B>
SOME ADDITIONAL BROWSABLE DIRECTORIES
</B></h3>
<P>
The Pop-11 and AI teaching and documentation files previously included
in the
<a href="oldcontents.html#bhamteach">bhamteach tar package</a> and now
part of the
