<a href="poplog.info.html#ctbook">http://www.cs.bham.ac.uk/research/poplog/poplog.info.html#ctbook</a>
<li>Larry Paulson's book
<a href="contrib/pml/WorkingProgrammer">ML for the Working
Programmer</a>,
